dmca.title: Re: Takedown Demand per DMCA 17 USC 512(c)
dmca.body:
Attn: [Private], Voyager.Net:
Attn: CoreComm Copyright Infringement Agent:

Demand is hereby made for takedown of http://www.millstreetdesign.com
based on copyright infringement. This website is using at least twelve
images which are copyright registered with the US Copyright Office by
Leslie A. Kelly, Doyle Yoder or Carol Highsmith. I aver that I am
authorized to represent Doyle Yoder, Carol Highsmith and Leslie A.
Kelly, in this demand regarding his copyright registrations which
are noted herein.

In accordance with the Digital Millennium Copyright Act, 17 USC
